==English==
===Combining form===
'''-wear'''

#Used to form nouns denoting clothing worn by a particular sex (eg, [[menswear]]) or age of person (eg, [[kidswear]]), on a particular part of the body (eg, [[neckwear]]), for a particular use (eg, [[daywear]]), made in a particular way (eg, [[knitwear]]) or (redundantly) of a particular kind (eg, [[shoewear]]).

